    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>When you hit a creature with a weapon attack, you can expend a spell slot to deal &amp;reference[force] damage and attempt to burden the target, in addition to the weapon's damage.</p><p><strong>Strength Save</strong> </p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 2d6]] force damage* and the target's speeds are halved.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 2d6]] force damage, no other effect.*</p></li></ul><p>*<strong>Using Higher Level Spell Slots</strong> : Damage increases by [[/damage 1d6 force]]{1d6} for each spell level above 1st.</p>",
